    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just a feeling though. i did the math today. if i'm gone, the life insurance or whatever might actually help and they wouldn't have to worry about my mistakes anymore. it's like, the only way i can actually help them now is to stop being the problem. doesn't that make sense?",
